snippet.title: FIFA 14 - PSP Gameplay (4K60fps)
snippet.description:
FIFA 14 - PSP Gameplay (4K60fps).

FIFA 14 is a sports association football simulation video game developed by EA Canada and published by EA Sports. It was released in September 2013 for the PlayStation 2, PlayStation 3, PlayStation Portable, PlayStation Vita, Xbox 360, Wii, Nintendo 3DS and Microsoft Windows.
